UID:BzGfVzYxspYP2UiQgpnby
SUMMARY:PhinneyWood Business Initiative Q&A
DTSTAMP:20260403T051040Z
DTSTART:20260407T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the PNA to ask your questions about the BIA and what
	 it means for the PhinneyWood business district This initiative represents
	 a community-led effort to create a sustainable\\\, long-term framework fo
	r supporting and strengthening the neighborhood’s business district—built 
	and guided by the people who live and invest here. \\nRSVP HERE: PhinneyWo
	od Business Initiative Meeting RSVP – Fill out form \\nPlease note this me
	eting is intended for property owners and business owners. A meeting for t
	he general public will be forthcoming at a later date. \\nQuestions? Pleas
	e reach out to the PNA’s Small Business Advocate\\\, Chris Maykut at chris
	m@phinneycenter.org\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/phinneywood-bus
	iness-initiative-qa/\n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
