BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ftoV-du-3SPVCdw4z6qQn
SUMMARY:Seattle Now & Then
DTSTAMP:20260403T051040Z
DTSTART:20260408T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday\\\, April 8. 1-2pm. GSC. Free. \\nNow & Then\\\, the 
	photo history column in the Seattle Times\\\, has been running since 1982.
	 Join columnists Jean Sherrard and Clay Eals as they share photos\\\, past
	 columns\\\, behind-the-scenes stories\\\, and Seattle history. RSVP: 206-
